title: HP Envy 13: Real-Life Review + Travel With Me!
description:
Sharing how I use my HP Envy 13 in my everyday life!

HP ENVY 13-d040nr 13-Inch Laptop (Core i7, 8 GB RAM, 256 SSD, Non-Touch Screen): http://amzn.to/2eTq7Es

♡My favorite specs about the HP Envy 13♡
♡ Weighs less than 2 lbs!!!
♡ So chic, lovw the aluminum body on the HP Envy 14
♡ Amazing HD display, great for watching movies & YouTube videos 
♡ Microsoft Hello Fingerprint Recognition 

This HP Envy 13 is such a cool laptop and would make such a great gift for anyone, including yourself! It's quick, light-weight, and so portable. It's great for anyone on the go that needs a great laptop! 




Check out my video on the HP Powerup Backpack! https://youtu.be/0qVkp7J5pH0

Thanks for watching!! Love y'all! Thumbs up if you enjoyed this video on my HP Envy 13, & PLEASE SUBSCRIBE for more videos!! ♡♡♡
